The paper deals with optimization problems and heuristics, which are common topics in computer science. The multidimensional assignment problem is a combinatorial optimization problem, which falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The use of heuristics to solve the problem suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and operations research (cs.OR). The empirical evaluation of the heuristics involves analyzing the results of computational experiments, which is a common practice in data mining (cs.DM) and scientific computing (cs.CC).
